#Q What is Apple's flagship product（旗舰产品）?
#A iphone and Mac book are Apple's flagship products.

#Q what do we often use to capture footage（拍摄视频） in our daily lives?
#A we often use our smart phone to capture footage in our daily life.

#Q what do children have the most faith in（对...有信心）?
#A their parents would be the one they'd trust most.

#Q what natural disaster often sweeps away（扫除掉） buildings?
#A an earthquake would often sweep away buildings.

#Q how do powerful individuals（有权的个人） often try to deal with scandals（丑闻）?
#A they often try to sweep them away（扫除障碍）, or hush them up（噤声）.